{
  "stem": "10587.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pesach was a very special holiday in our house because we-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we should fall asleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The services were conducted and the songs were sang such a long time that most-- my younger brother and I, we always fell asleep.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it was a very cheerful type of a holiday, with many songs and asking the four questions, which I always volunteered to be the first one to ask the-- the four questions, which are called the [YIDDISH].",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] it was a very festive holiday in our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother used to work quite a bit to cook their meals and to prepare the dishes to make them kosher for Pesach, and boil them in water in big pots.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And it was quite a-- a busy time in-- in our home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was also a very special time, a lot of anticipation of Pesach, of the Seder.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And it was a-- It was a long holiday because we used to have two Seders, and then have the [HEBREW].",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was a festive as well as a religious holiday.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We were sitting at the table and all I remember, that took a long time for the Seders to-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] to complete the Seders.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It used to be very late at night.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So I know that my younger brother definitely, and I myself, fell sleep most of the time at the end.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We never finished it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So-- but it was a very important holiday [INAUDIBLE] in my home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My-- my-- well, my grandfather was a widower.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he would eat a Pesach.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember he used to come to us quite often.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
